There's a video of someone saying "Hi" to Makani, one of the Orcas at the SeaWorld in San Diego, in such a range. He picked up that tone immediately, and repeated it back to the girl.  They problem solve, and pick things up at the very least 20Ã— quicker than humans can. They are incredibly intelligent. I know that you know how intelligent they are.
